      <hedline>
        <hl1>'Spell ''World'' Backward'</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Bernard Cooper's Lives column (Jan. 8) prompted a pleasant memory of my mother under similar circumstances. She was asked to name (in reverse chronological order) the presidents and vice presidents as far back as she could remember. With dismay, she stopped at Nixon's vice president, having drawn a blank. The doctor chuckled. ''You're off the hook,'' he said. ''I can't remember, either.''</p>
        <p>Ellen Rosichan</p>
        <p>Miami Beach</p>
      </block>
